      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那这个包结构是按比特位来划分吗？比如0-15位是源端口，16-31位是目的端口这种？另外\"Education_ContentCDN\"和\"Education_ClassroomService\"是放在选项字段还是数据区？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "0-15",
        "16-31",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，按比特位划分。Education_ContentCDN放在160-191位，作为选项字段；Education_ClassroomService放在192-255位的数据区。这样设计是为了演示教育内容分发网络和课堂服务在协议栈中的不同层级。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "160-191",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "192-255",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出标准TCP头部：0-31位是源端口和目的端口，32-95位是序列号和确认号。控制位部分URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN分别放在106-111位，Window在112-127位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number",
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
