        "FIN",
        "Window",
        "112-127"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "控制位的顺序确认一下：URG是紧急标志，ACK是确认标志，这个顺序别搞反了。还有Checksum和Urgent Pointer的位置也要标清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认了，106位URG，107位ACK，128-143位Checksum，144-159位Urgent Pointer。现在加上教育相关的字段：160-191位标注为Education_ContentCDN，192-255位是Data，里面承载Education_ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
